MarkstX is similar to LaTeX, meaning you define the document structure and layout via plain-text and then it is compiled into the final document.

Unlike LaTeX, MarkstX uses the power of markdown to allow an easier syntax for simple markup of text. But brings more functionality with the additional syntax and templating system.

### Migrating From Markdown
If you have a lot of documents already written in markdown, it is easy to convert them into a MarkstX document. It is mostly just copy-n-paste. Take a look on how to create a document to learn more.
